Detailed Description

RNAStructAlignmentML -- XML representation of rna secondary structure alignments, uses dotBracket

Namespace : NAMESPACE XSD-Schema : NSLOCATION

Author:
Kai Loewenthal <kloewent@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de>
Version:
1.0 TODO : 1) Current version does not implement crossrefs!
Exceptions:
BioDOMException on failure / fatal error
